<item>
            <title>[FLINK-3478] Flink serves arbitary files through the web interface</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-3478</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Flink serves arbitrary files through the web server of the 8081 port, e.g. &lt;tt&gt;../../../../../../../../../../etc/passwd&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The requested path needs to be validated before it is served.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
